OH, OKAY.
JUST LOOK IN THE HALL.

15:27.375 --> 15:28.375
YEAH ?

15:28.375 --> 15:29.667
JUST LOOK OUT
IN THE HALL.

15:29.667 --> 15:31.333
[ Chuckle ]

15:31.333 --> 15:32.083
OKAY.

15:34.542 --> 15:36.917
[ Chuckle ]

15:36.917 --> 15:38.583
THAT'S A BABY.

15:38.583 --> 15:40.166
I KNOW
IT'S A BABY.

15:40.166 --> 15:41.500
WHAT'S IT
DOING THERE ?

15:41.500 --> 15:43.333
IT'S SLEEPING.

15:43.333 --> 15:46.208
WHO DO YOU SUPPOSE
IT BELONGS TO ?

15:46.208 --> 15:49.291
PETER, THERE'S A NOTE.

15:50.667 --> 15:53.375
ALL RIGHT,
I'LL JUST PLAY ALONG.

15:58.625 --> 16:01.375
"DEAR JACK, HERE IS OUR BABY."

16:01.375 --> 16:03.709
OH, NO.

16:03.709 --> 16:06.333
YOU REALLY DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT THIS ?

16:06.333 --> 16:09.417
I KNEW THIS WOULD HAPPEN
TO HIM SOONER OR LATER.

16:11.917 --> 16:13.875
"I CAN'T HANDLE THIS.
I DON'T KNOW WHERE TO TURN."

16:13.875 --> 16:15.041
RIGHT.

16:15.041 --> 16:17.959
"SOMEDAY I HOPE YOU
CAN BOTH FORGIVE ME.

16:17.959 --> 16:20.041
HER NAME IS MARY.
LOVE, SYLVIA."

16:20.041 --> 16:21.709
WHO'S SYLVIA ?

16:21.709 --> 16:24.917
YOU NEED A SECRETARY TO
KEEP TRACK OF ALL HIS WOMEN.

16:24.917 --> 16:27.458
HE LEFT A MESSAGE
ABOUT A PACKAGE ...

16:27.458 --> 16:28.792
BEING DELIVERED TODAY.

16:28.792 --> 16:30.875
HE SAID TO PUT IT ASIDE
AND NOT WORRY ABOUT IT.

16:30.875 --> 16:32.000
HE SAID THAT
ABOUT A BABY ?

16:32.000 --> 16:34.000
HE TAKES PROCREATION
A LITTLE LIGHTLY.

16:34.000 --> 16:36.208
WHAT ARE WE
SUPPOSED TO DO ?

16:36.208 --> 16:37.667
PICK IT UP.

16:37.667 --> 16:39.125
YOU PICK IT UP.

16:39.125 --> 16:40.542
I'M NOT PICKING IT UP !

16:40.542 --> 16:41.250
YOU FOUND IT !

16:41.250 --> 16:47.500
[ Baby Cries ]

16:47.500 --> 16:49.792
ONE OF US HAS
TO PICK IT UP.

16:49.792 --> 16:51.375
IT'S NOT
GOING TO BE ME.

16:51.375 --> 16:54.458
[ Baby Cries Louder ]

16:54.458 --> 17:00.792
[ Crying Continues ]

17:00.792 --> 17:03.583
I DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT BABIES.

17:03.583 --> 17:05.250
NEITHER DO I.

17:05.250 --> 17:07.791
WE'VE GOT TO
DO SOMETHING.
BE MY GUEST.

17:07.791 --> 17:09.709
IT'S NOT MY
RESPONSIBILITY.

17:09.709 --> 17:10.666
IT'S NOT MINE,
EITHER.

17:10.666 --> 17:12.541
DON'T YELL
AT ME !

17:12.541 --> 17:14.165
IT CAN'T BE
THAT DIFFICULT.

17:14.165 --> 17:16.165
JUST FEED IT.
IT'LL SHUT UP.

17:16.165 --> 17:17.375
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT BABIES EAT !

17:17.375 --> 17:18.959
SOFT STUFF.

17:18.959 --> 17:21.750
WE WERE BABIES ONCE.
WHAT DID WE EAT ?

17:21.750 --> 17:24.375
IT COULDN'T HAVE BEEN
VERY GOOD; I CAN'T REMEMBER.

17:27.375 --> 17:29.166
WAIT !
WHERE
ARE YOU GOING ?

17:29.166 --> 17:33.375
TO GET BABY FOOD. WE CAN'T
FEED IT CAKE AND GOAT CHEESE.

17:33.375 --> 17:34.500
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO ?

17:34.500 --> 17:36.667
ENTERTAIN IT.

17:36.667 --> 17:37.792
"ENTERTAIN IT !"

17:37.792 --> 17:43.041
[ Baby Still Crying ]

17:43.041 --> 17:44.792
HOW DO YOU
ENTERTAIN A BABY ?

17:44.792 --> 17:47.625
HEY, JUNIOR.

17:47.625 --> 17:49.000
LOOK AT MY HANDS.

17:49.000 --> 17:51.625
[ Baby Still Crying ]

17:51.625 --> 17:52.709
LOOK AT THIS.

17:52.709 --> 17:54.917
IT'S A GLASS; A PRISM.

17:54.917 --> 17:56.500
LOOK AT THOSE COLORS.

17:56.500 --> 17:58.500
THIS IS NICE;
EXPENSIVE.

17:58.500 --> 17:59.834
YOU DON'T LIKE THAT.

17:59.834 --> 18:01.667
HOW ABOUT ... OH, LOOK.

18:01.667 --> 18:04.750
IT'S ALMOST LIKE
JAPANESE ORIGAMI !

18:04.750 --> 18:07.125
IT'S A BIRD !
IT'S A BIRD !

18:07.125 --> 18:07.875
NO, HUH ?

18:07.875 --> 18:10.834
[ Crying Continues ]

18:10.834 --> 18:12.333
I'M GETTING
A HEADACHE.

18:12.333 --> 18:14.000
YOU'RE GIVING
ME A HEADACHE.

18:14.000 --> 18:15.709
HOW ABOUT THIS ?

18:15.709 --> 18:17.542
A HAIRY CHEST !

18:17.542 --> 18:19.125
LIKE THAT ?
YOU WANT ONE OF THESE ?

18:23.750 --> 18:25.166
EXCUSE ME.

18:25.166 --> 18:26.875
WHERE CAN I GET
A JAR OF BABY FOOD ?

18:26.875 --> 18:28.333
3rd AISLE
TO THE RIGHT.

18:28.333 --> 18:30.125
RIGHT.

18:46.458 --> 18:48.375
THEY GOTTA
BE KIDDING.

18:48.375 --> 18:49.959
[ Talking Jive ]
WHAT'S HAPPENING, BABY ?

18:49.959 --> 18:51.375
HOW YOU DOING TODAY ?

18:51.375 --> 18:54.166
MY NAME IS JOHNNY.

18:54.166 --> 18:56.959
THAT'S RIGHT, BUT YOU
CAN CALL ME MR. COOL.

18:56.959 --> 18:59.375
WHAT'S YOUR NAME ?

18:59.375 --> 19:01.667
HAVEN'T I SEEN YOU
AROUND THE NEIGHBORHOOD ?

19:01.667 --> 19:02.959
WHAT'S THE MATTER ?

19:02.959 --> 19:04.250
CAT GOT YOUR TONGUE ?

19:04.250 --> 19:06.125
WHY CAN'T YOU TALK ?

19:08.625 --> 19:10.125
[ Baby Still Crying ]

19:10.125 --> 19:13.917
COME ON, KID.
I'M DOING MY BEST.

19:23.667 --> 19:24.917
EXCUSE ME.

19:24.917 --> 19:26.333
IS THIS A GOOD MEAL
FOR A BABY ?

19:26.333 --> 19:29.083
THAT'S FOR TODDLERS.
WHAT'S A TODDLER ?

19:29.083 --> 19:30.458
1 1/2 TO 2 YEARS.

19:30.458 --> 19:32.542
I NEED SOMETHING
FOR A BABY.

19:32.542 --> 19:33.750
THIS IS
YOUR FIRST ?

19:33.750 --> 19:35.125
FIRST WHAT ?
BABY.

19:35.125 --> 19:38.250
YEAH.
FIRST AND LAST.

19:38.250 --> 19:41.375
NO MATTER HOW YOU PREPARE,
YOU'RE NEVER READY.

19:41.375 --> 19:42.458
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

19:42.458 --> 19:43.834
WHAT AN INFANT EATS ...

19:43.834 --> 19:45.333
CAN YOU --

19:45.333 --> 19:48.542
CAN DETERMINE ITS
ENTIRE FUTURE.

19:48.542 --> 19:51.709
THAT'S FASCINATING,
BUT ALL I NEED IS FOOD.

19:51.709 --> 19:53.917
THAT'S ALL.

19:53.917 --> 19:55.291
WHAT'S THE BEST
SELLING BRAND ?

19:55.291 --> 19:57.792
THAT WHITE CAN.

19:57.792 --> 19:59.291
THIS IS THE BEST ?

19:59.291 --> 20:01.000
NO, IT'S THE CHEAPEST.
THAT'S WHY IT SELLS.

20:02.125 --> 20:03.291
HOW ABOUT
THIS ONE ?

20:03.291 --> 20:04.667
THAT'S GOOD,

20:04.667 --> 20:06.750
BUT IT'S GOT
IRON IN IT.

20:06.750 --> 20:07.959
IS THAT BAD ?

20:07.959 --> 20:09.667
IF YOUR BABY'S
ALLERGIC TO IT.

20:09.667 --> 20:11.333
HOW DO YOU KNOW
IF SHE'S ALLERGIC ?

20:11.333 --> 20:13.041
THEY THROW UP
ALL OVER YOU.

20:13.041 --> 20:16.333
BUT THEY THROW UP EVEN
IF THEY'RE NOT ALLERGIC.

20:16.333 --> 20:19.792
SOME BABIES CAN'T
HOLD ANYTHING DOWN.

20:19.792 --> 20:21.750
WHAT ABOUT THIS ONE ?

20:21.750 --> 20:23.542
THAT'S FOR OLDER BABIES.

20:23.542 --> 20:26.333
HOW OLD IS YOUR BABY ?

20:28.166 --> 20:29.667
ABOUT THAT OLD.

20:29.667 --> 20:31.542
YOU DON'T KNOW HOW
OLD YOUR BABY IS ?

20:31.542 --> 20:33.166
YES I DO.

20:33.166 --> 20:35.667
IS SHE TEETHING ?
TEETHING ?

20:35.667 --> 20:40.625
DOES SHE CRY ALL NIGHT,
CHEW HER FIST AND DROOL ?

20:40.625 --> 20:43.041
ALL RIGHT, I'LL
TAKE 3 OF THESE,

20:43.041 --> 20:45.542
AND SOME OF THESE --

20:45.542 --> 20:47.375
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME.

20:48.750 --> 20:51.542
YOU'VE BEEN A SOURCE
OF GREAT DISTRESS.

20:51.542 --> 20:53.750
IF SHE'S LESS THAN
3 MONTHS OLD,

20:53.750 --> 20:56.041
YOU'VE GOT TO
STERILIZE THE NIPPLES.

21:01.375 --> 21:03.709
[ Imitating Bubbling Sounds
While Baby Cries ]

21:03.709 --> 21:05.959
HERE IT COMES.

21:05.959 --> 21:12.834
[ Crying Continues ]

21:12.834 --> 21:15.041
HEY !
LOOK !

21:15.041 --> 21:17.041
I'LL GIVE YOU $10
IF YOU STOP CRYING.

21:17.041 --> 21:18.458
$10 BUCKS, HUH ?

21:18.458 --> 21:20.709
[ Crying ]

21:20.709 --> 21:22.875
I'M GOING TO
PICK YOU UP, NOW.

21:22.875 --> 21:25.125
THERE YOU GO, JR.

21:25.125 --> 21:27.542
IS THAT BETTER ?

21:27.542 --> 21:31.500
HOW ABOUT A
LITTLE WALK ?

21:31.500 --> 21:33.667
WAIT A MINUTE.

21:33.667 --> 21:37.083
OKAY.
HEY,
HOW ABOUT THIS ?

21:37.083 --> 21:40.250
NO, WE'RE NOT GOING
TO KEEP CRYING.

21:40.250 --> 21:42.333
[ Crying Continues ]

21:42.333 --> 21:44.125
NO, NO, WAIT.

21:44.125 --> 21:47.417
â™ª ROCK-A-BYE BABY
ON THE TREE TOP â™ª

21:47.417 --> 21:51.083
â™ª WHEN THE BOUGH BREAKS
NA-NA-NA-NA-NA â™ª

21:51.083 --> 21:53.083
â™ª SOMETHING LIKE
LAUGHING -- â™ª

21:53.083 --> 21:55.083
COME ON !
WHERE THE HELL IS HE ?

21:55.083 --> 21:56.792
MILKING THE COWS
OR SOMETHING ?

21:56.792 --> 21:59.125
LOOK !
NO CRYING.

21:59.125 --> 22:01.291
HEY WAIT A MINUTE !

22:01.291 --> 22:03.333
YOU CAN DRIVE
A GUY TO DRINK.

22:03.333 --> 22:06.917
NO, NOT YOU.
YOU'RE A CUTE LITTLE THING.

22:06.917 --> 22:08.583
HOW ABOUT:

22:08.583 --> 22:10.792
â™ª HUSH LITTLE BABY
DON'T YOU CRY â™ª

22:10.792 --> 22:14.417
â™ª WHEN PETER GETS HOME, I'M
GONNA PUNCH HIM IN THE EYE â™ª

22:14.417 --> 22:17.041
ALL RIGHT, HERE WE ARE.

22:17.041 --> 22:19.375
HERE WE ARE IN MY ROOM.

22:19.375 --> 22:22.959
LOOK AROUND HERE.
THIS IS NICE, HUH ?

22:22.959 --> 22:25.750
WE'LL SIT DOWN HERE.

22:25.750 --> 22:28.250
LOOK !
WE'RE GOING
TO WATCH A LITTLE TV.

22:28.250 --> 22:31.917
YEAH, JUST YOU AND ME.

22:31.917 --> 22:34.917
HERE YOU GO.

22:34.917 --> 22:36.500
AMUSE YOURSELF.

22:36.500 --> 22:40.667
WOMEN ARE WONDERING,
ARE THEY HAVING AN ORGASM ?

22:40.667 --> 22:43.291
[ Crying Stops ]
MEN ARE WORRIED MAYBE
THEIR PENIS --

22:43.291 --> 22:45.083
WHOA, WHOA.

22:45.083 --> 22:47.875
NO, YOU DON'T
WANT TO HEAR THAT.

22:47.875 --> 22:48.959
[ Doorbell ]

22:50.583 --> 22:52.917
WE'LL HAVE A NICE CONVERSATION
WITH UNCLE PETER ...

22:52.917 --> 22:55.041
AND LET HIM
HAVE SOME FUN.

22:55.041 --> 22:57.125
THAT'S A GOOD IDEA.

22:57.125 --> 22:58.625
WHERE THE HELL
HAVE YOU BEEN ?

22:58.625 --> 23:01.375
OH, HI,
MRS. HATHAWAY.

23:01.375 --> 23:04.375
OH, WHAT A DARLING
LITTLE BABY !

23:04.375 --> 23:05.917
IS IT YOURS ?

23:05.917 --> 23:08.250
NO, IT'S NOT MINE.
MR. MITCHELL'S ?

23:08.250 --> 23:11.041
NO, SOMEONE
LOANED IT TO US.

23:11.041 --> 23:13.041
WE'RE WATCHING
HER FOR A WHILE.

23:13.041 --> 23:14.333
WHAT'S ITS NAME ?

23:14.333 --> 23:17.166
ITS NAME IS UH,
UH, SYLVIA.

23:17.166 --> 23:19.458
NO, MARY, MARY.

23:19.458 --> 23:22.458
WE'VE HAD A TOUGH MORNING,
AND WE'RE TUCKERED OUT.

23:22.458 --> 23:27.041
WE HAVE TO SAY GOOD-BYE.
BYE-BYE, MRS. HATHAWAY.

23:28.750 --> 23:30.959
BY THE WAY,

23:30.959 --> 23:33.333
THIS PACKAGE JUST ARRIVED
FOR YOU DOWNSTAIRS.

23:33.333 --> 23:36.166
[ Crying Continues ]

23:36.166 --> 23:38.041
ALL RIGHT,
GREAT.

23:38.041 --> 23:39.709
COULD I HOLD HER ?

23:39.709 --> 23:41.542
I DON'T THINK SO.

23:41.542 --> 23:43.125
I LOVE BABIES.

23:43.125 --> 23:46.542
OH, YES.
TCH, TCH, TCH.
[ Crying Stops ]

23:46.542 --> 23:49.250
I JUST
LOVE BABIES.

23:49.250 --> 23:51.083
UNFORTUNATELY,
MR. HATHAWAY AND I ...

23:51.083 --> 23:53.208
WERE NEVER ABLE
TO HAVE ANY.

23:53.208 --> 23:55.458
MR. HATHAWAY HAS A
LOW SPERM COUNT.

23:55.458 --> 23:58.041
SOME GUYS HAVE
ALL THE LUCK.

23:58.041 --> 24:02.250
OH, YOU ARE A CUTE
LITTLE BUNDLE, AREN'T YOU ?

24:04.500 --> 24:06.000
YOU DO REALIZE
SHE DID A DOODLE ?

24:06.000 --> 24:08.458
YES, YOU DID.

24:08.458 --> 24:10.792
WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO CHANGE HER ?

24:10.792 --> 24:13.667
NO, I CAN DO IT.

24:13.667 --> 24:15.834
I'M USED TO IT.

24:15.834 --> 24:18.208
THANKS, WE'VE
GOT TO GO NOW.

24:18.208 --> 24:21.125
WE'RE GONNA SAY
BYE-BYE, NOW.

24:21.125 --> 24:22.959
BYE-BYE.

24:22.959 --> 24:24.125
BYE-BYE.

24:24.125 --> 24:26.667
BYE-BYE-BYE.

24:26.667 --> 24:29.583
IF YOU EVER NEED
A BABY-SITTER --
[ Crying Begins Again ]

24:29.583 --> 24:31.417
ALL RIGHT,
THANKS.

24:31.417 --> 24:33.000
SHE'S A
LOVELY BABY.

24:33.000 --> 24:34.583
ADORABLE.

24:34.583 --> 24:36.417
THIS BABY HASN'T
STOPPED CRYING.

24:36.417 --> 24:38.250
SHE DID A DOODLE.

24:38.250 --> 24:39.959
WHAT THE
HELL IS THAT ?

24:39.959 --> 24:42.166
DON'T TELL ME.
I DON'T WANT TO KNOW.

24:42.166 --> 24:43.667
YOU'RE GONNA KNOW,
BECAUSE SHE DID IT.

24:43.667 --> 24:45.625
[ Crying Continues ]

24:45.625 --> 24:49.083
I HAD TO GO 3 PLACES
AND GET 4 KINDS OF FORMULA.

24:49.083 --> 24:53.375
2 KINDS OF DIAPERS,
BOTTLES, TOWELS, NIPPLES --

24:53.375 --> 24:56.250
YOU HAVE NO IDEA HOW
MUCH CRAP KIDS NEED.

24:56.250 --> 24:58.458
HOW OLD IS SHE ?

24:58.458 --> 25:00.750
YOU WANT ME TO CHECK
HER DRIVER'S LICENSE ?

25:00.750 --> 25:04.333
YOU CAN TELL HOW OLD SHE
IS BY FEELING HER TEETH.

25:04.333 --> 25:06.291
I'M NOT FEELING
HER TEETH !

25:06.291 --> 25:08.291
I'M TIRED OF
HOLDING HER.

25:08.291 --> 25:10.750
I CAN'T HOLD HER
AND MAKE HER BOTTLE.

25:10.750 --> 25:15.125
I'LL HOLD HER.
YOU CHECK THE TEETH.

25:15.125 --> 25:16.959
COME ON !

25:25.208 --> 25:26.208
I CAN'T FEEL ANYTHING.

25:26.208 --> 25:27.625
WHAT'S
THAT MEAN ?

25:27.625 --> 25:28.709
SHE DOESN'T
HAVE ANY TEETH !

25:28.709 --> 25:30.750
NEITHER DID GABBY HAYES,
AND HE WAS 90.

25:30.750 --> 25:32.750
WE'LL GIVE HER THE
STUFF FOR NEWBORNS ...

25:32.750 --> 25:34.458
AND HOPE SHE'S
NOT ALLERGIC.

25:34.458 --> 25:36.959
YOU'VE NO IDEA WHAT
THEY CAN BE ALLERGIC TO.

25:36.959 --> 25:38.458
WHAT'S THAT STENCH ?

25:38.458 --> 25:41.375
[ Crying Has Stopped ]
HOLD HER.

25:41.375 --> 25:43.041
JUST HOLD HER.

25:43.041 --> 25:45.125
THIS IS A GIRL.
SHOULD WE BE DOING THIS ?

25:45.125 --> 25:47.000
JUST HOLD HER, SO I
CAN GET THE DIAPER OFF.

25:48.583 --> 25:50.709
OHH !
AWWW !

25:50.709 --> 25:52.583
HOW COULD SOMETHING
SO SMALL ...

25:52.583 --> 25:55.000
CREATE SOMETHING
SO DISGUSTING ?

25:55.000 --> 25:57.208
BEATS THE SHIT
OUT OF ME.

25:57.208 --> 25:58.709
HAND ME THE
OTHER DIAPER.

25:58.709 --> 26:00.083
OH !

26:00.083 --> 26:01.834
SHOULDN'T WE
WASH HER ?

26:01.834 --> 26:03.542
WE'LL WASH
HER LATER.

26:03.542 --> 26:04.834
GET ME
THE COTTON.

26:04.834 --> 26:06.667
OH !

26:06.667 --> 26:08.500
HERE IT IS.

26:09.667 --> 26:11.333
JUST GIVE ME
A LITTLE COTTON.

26:11.333 --> 26:13.834
I DON'T NEED
A PACKAGE.

26:13.834 --> 26:16.917
GET ME THE
COTTON WIPIES.

26:21.291 --> 26:23.667
[ Groans ]

26:25.333 --> 26:27.291
THIS IS
DISGUSTING.

26:27.291 --> 26:28.875
IT'S ALL OVER
AND IT'S STICKY.

26:30.917 --> 26:33.834
WE'RE GOING TO NEED SOME
KIND OF CLEANING FLUID.

26:33.834 --> 26:35.417
HOW ABOUT
AFTER-SHAVE ?

26:35.417 --> 26:38.417
COME ON, MICHAEL,
JUST GET A DIAPER.

26:39.709 --> 26:41.542
OH !

26:43.875 --> 26:46.333
DO THESE TAPES GO
IN FRONT OR BACK ?

26:46.333 --> 26:47.625
HOW AM I
SUPPOSED TO KNOW ?

26:49.458 --> 26:52.166
THESE ARE
WAY TOO BIG !

26:52.166 --> 26:55.625
WHAT SIZE
DID YOU GET ?
THEY'RE ULTRA
ABSORBENT.

26:55.625 --> 26:57.625
THE MORE ABSORBENT,
THE BETTER !

26:57.625 --> 27:00.667
HOLD HER !
SHE'S GOING CRAZY.

27:00.667 --> 27:02.667
I DON'T WANT TO.
COME ON,
MICHAEL !

27:02.667 --> 27:05.291
YOU'RE GOING
TO RIP IT.
I'M NOT GOING
TO RIP IT.

27:05.291 --> 27:07.208
YES, YOU ARE.
[ Rip ]

27:07.208 --> 27:09.542
GET ME
ANOTHER DIAPER.

27:09.542 --> 27:12.333
I'LL USE THE TAPE.
I'LL TAPE IT UP.

27:12.333 --> 27:14.667
I'M AN ARCHITECT,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKE.

27:14.667 --> 27:16.750
I BUILD 50-STORY
SKYSCRAPERS.

27:16.750 --> 27:18.875
I ASSEMBLE CITIES
OF THE FUTURE.

27:18.875 --> 27:21.083
I CAN CERTAINLY PUT
TOGETHER A GODDAMN DIAPER.

27:21.083 --> 27:22.458
TAKE IT EASY, KID.

27:24.750 --> 27:28.458
THERE, SEE ?

27:28.458 --> 27:31.750
IT'S WORKING.
A PIECE OF CAKE.

27:31.750 --> 27:33.083
YEAH.

27:33.083 --> 27:34.917
NICE JOB, PETE.

27:37.250 --> 27:39.792
[ Dribbling Sound ]

27:46.250 --> 27:48.667
THE LITTLE INSECT
WAS JUST WAITING ...

27:48.667 --> 27:51.333
FOR THAT DIAPER
TO FALL OFF.

27:51.333 --> 27:53.208
I THINK WE'RE
IN TROUBLE.

27:53.208 --> 27:56.500
[ Baby Gurgles ]

28:00.834 --> 28:03.291
I'M GOING TO
KILL JACK.

28:05.959 --> 28:07.166
I'M GOING
TO KILL HIM.

28:09.959 --> 28:11.542
[ Gagging Sound ]

28:17.583 --> 28:19.458
THIS IS THE DEAL.

28:19.458 --> 28:20.875
MICHAEL.
WHAT ?

28:20.875 --> 28:23.417
YOU'RE GOING TO HAVE TO
WASH WHERE THE POOP WAS.

28:23.417 --> 28:25.125
COME ON.

28:25.125 --> 28:27.000
ALL RIGHTY.

28:27.000 --> 28:30.000
YOU'RE NOT GETTING
ANYTHING OFF THAT WAY.

28:32.417 --> 28:36.834
THERE YOU GO.
THAT'S CLEAN.

28:36.834 --> 28:38.750
I'LL RINSE HER.

28:38.750 --> 28:40.542
RINSE HER
A LITTLE BIT.

28:40.542 --> 28:42.583
THERE WE GO.

28:42.583 --> 28:45.083
THIS IS FOR
MOISTURIZING --

28:45.083 --> 28:47.500
DON'T USE THE
BABY LOTION NOW.

28:47.500 --> 28:50.000
IT SAYS,
"PREVENTS CHAPPING."

28:50.000 --> 28:51.625
JUST WASH HER.

28:51.625 --> 28:54.208
I'LL PUT SOME IN
JUST TO MAKE SURE.

28:57.625 --> 29:02.166
[ Baby Babbling ]

29:08.667 --> 29:10.333
[ Pooping Sound ]

29:10.333 --> 29:12.083
[ Baby Begins Crying ]

29:29.458 --> 29:32.959
[ Baby Making Contented Noises ]

30:00.458 --> 30:02.375
WE GOTTA GET
SOME HELP.

30:02.375 --> 30:06.417
JACK SAID THIS IS A
DELICATE SITUATION,

30:06.417 --> 30:08.834
THAT WE SHOULDN'T
TELL ANYBODY.

30:08.834 --> 30:11.667
CAN YOU BELIEVE HIM
PUTTING US THROUGH HELL ...

30:11.667 --> 30:14.458
TO SAVE HIS
PRECIOUS REPUTATION ?

30:14.458 --> 30:16.333
I'M NOT DOING
IT, ANYMORE.

30:16.333 --> 30:19.709
[ Baby Begins To Cry ]

30:19.709 --> 30:20.834
ODDS.

30:51.000 --> 30:53.875
[ Siren Approaching ]

31:41.834 --> 31:43.667
[ Clunk ]

31:43.667 --> 31:46.709
YOU'RE GOING TO
HAVE A HEADACHE.

31:46.709 --> 31:50.750
MARY, LET ME
HAVE THE PEN.

31:50.750 --> 31:54.625
I'M LATER THAN USUAL
FOR THE DEADLINE.

31:54.625 --> 31:57.667
COME HERE.
OKAY ?

32:06.542 --> 32:09.250
ACTUALLY, I DON'T SEEM
TO HAVE THEM AFTER ALL.

32:09.250 --> 32:11.625
I MUST HAVE LEFT
THEM AT THE OFFICE.

32:11.625 --> 32:13.291
I'LL GET THEM
IN THE MORNING.

32:13.291 --> 32:15.709
RIGHT.

32:15.709 --> 32:18.750
YOUR DADDY'S
A DEAD MAN.

32:18.750 --> 32:19.917
[ Ding ]

32:24.375 --> 32:26.458
[ Doorbell ]

32:26.458 --> 32:27.875
[ Knocking ]

32:27.875 --> 32:29.875
REBECCA YOU'RE --

32:29.875 --> 32:31.208
I CAME AS SOON
AS I COULD.

32:31.208 --> 32:32.834
WHO ARE YOU ?

32:32.834 --> 32:36.000
THIS IS JAN CLOPATZ;
PETER MITCHELL.

32:36.000 --> 32:37.959
HOW DO YOU DO.

32:37.959 --> 32:40.709
JAN IS A CELLIST
FROM HUNGARY.

32:40.709 --> 32:43.500
HE'S PLAYING AT
CARNEGIE HALL.

32:43.500 --> 32:45.417
WHAT A THRILL.

32:45.417 --> 32:46.792
WHAT'S THE
EMERGENCY ?

32:46.792 --> 32:48.750
JUST COME
WITH ME.

32:50.417 --> 32:53.583
THIS IS THE
BIG EMERGENCY.

32:56.542 --> 32:57.917
IT'S A BABY.

32:57.917 --> 33:00.208
WHY'S THAT THE FIRST
THING EVERYBODY SAYS ?

33:00.208 --> 33:01.417
OF COURSE
IT'S A BABY.

33:01.417 --> 33:02.959
IT'S YOUR BABY ?

33:02.959 --> 33:05.041
IT'S NOT MINE.
IT'S JACK'S.

33:05.041 --> 33:06.083
JACK HAS
A BABY ?

33:06.083 --> 33:08.834
I REALIZE THAT
TENDS TO NEGATE ...

33:08.834 --> 33:10.917
OUR BELIEF IN A
BENEVOLENT GOD.

33:10.917 --> 33:13.125
IT DOESN'T LOOK LIKE JACK.
HE HAS MORE HAIR.

33:13.125 --> 33:15.166
I'M GLAD YOU CAN JOKE
AT A TIME LIKE THIS.

33:15.166 --> 33:17.166
SHE NEEDS
TO BE HELD.

33:17.166 --> 33:19.333
BABIES LIKE
TO BE HELD.

33:19.333 --> 33:20.291
WHERE IS HE ?

33:20.291 --> 33:22.250
JACK'S IN TURKEY,

33:22.250 --> 33:24.709
WHICH IS WHERE I'D BE
IF MY BABY WAS IN NEW YORK.

33:24.709 --> 33:26.792
WE'RE DYING HERE.

33:26.792 --> 33:29.000
MICHAEL DOESN'T
KNOW ABOUT BABIES.

33:29.000 --> 33:30.625
I DON'T KNOW
ABOUT BABIES.

33:30.625 --> 33:33.333
I'VE GOT DEADLINES
HANGING ALL OVER ME.

33:33.333 --> 33:36.667
I'VE BEEN READING
BOOKS ABOUT BABIES.

33:36.667 --> 33:38.834
I CAN'T FIGURE
IT OUT.

33:38.834 --> 33:41.625
IT SAYS,
"FEED EVERY 2 HOURS."

33:41.625 --> 33:44.208
IT TAKES ME 2 HOURS
TO GET HER TO EAT.

33:44.208 --> 33:48.291
DOES IT MEAN 2 HOURS FROM
WHEN I START OR FINISH ?

33:48.291 --> 33:50.959
I'VE BEEN FEEDING
HER FROM WHEN I START,

33:50.959 --> 33:53.208
AND I'M FEEDING
HER ALL THE TIME.

33:53.208 --> 33:55.625
WHICH IS IT ?

33:55.625 --> 33:58.000
WHY ARE YOU
ASKING ME ?
YOU'RE A WOMAN.

33:58.000 --> 34:01.041
THAT DOESN'T MEAN
I KNOW ABOUT BABIES.

34:01.041 --> 34:03.041
REBECCA --

34:04.583 --> 34:07.917
PLEASE STAY WITH ME, AND
HELP ME TAKE CARE OF HER.

34:07.917 --> 34:09.792
YOU WANT ME TO
TAKE CARE OF HER ?

34:09.792 --> 34:12.041
YES.
NOW ?

34:12.041 --> 34:13.000
NO, WHEN SHE
GRADUATES FROM COLLEGE.

34:13.000 --> 34:14.458
YES, NOW.

34:14.458 --> 34:16.792
I CAN'T DO THAT.

34:16.792 --> 34:21.333
BABY TAKE ...
VERY, VERY MUCH WORK.

34:21.333 --> 34:24.750
THANKS FOR TELLING ME.
IS HE AN IDIOT SAVANT ?

34:24.750 --> 34:26.041
REBECCA, WE BE LATE.

34:29.083 --> 34:31.500
REBECCA --

34:31.500 --> 34:34.000
REBECCA,
PLEASE.

34:35.625 --> 34:37.333
STAY WITH ME.

34:37.333 --> 34:39.792
I HAVE GOT
A DATE !

34:39.792 --> 34:45.083
EXCUSE ME FOR CRAMPING
YOUR ROMANTIC STYLE.

34:45.083 --> 34:47.000
REBECCA, WE BE LATE !

34:47.000 --> 34:49.875
YOU CAN'T BE
SERIOUS ABOUT HIM.

34:49.875 --> 34:52.792
YOU GO OUT WITH
OTHER PEOPLE; SO DO I.

34:52.792 --> 34:55.917
I DON'T CARE IF YOU DATE
THE WHOLE STRING SECTION.

34:55.917 --> 34:58.542
RIGHT NOW,
I NEED YOU.
I CAN'T BE
HERE NOW.

34:58.542 --> 35:00.208
OH, SHE DOODLED !

35:00.208 --> 35:01.917
DOODLED.

35:01.917 --> 35:03.417
YES, DOODLED !

35:03.417 --> 35:05.125
DON'T BABIES
DOODLE IN HUNGARY ?

35:05.125 --> 35:06.375
WE'RE LEAVING.

35:06.375 --> 35:07.709
REBECCA !

35:07.709 --> 35:09.834
WAIT.

35:09.834 --> 35:11.375
COME ON, REBECCA.

35:11.375 --> 35:13.208
DON'T GO.

35:13.208 --> 35:15.709
YOU'RE A
VERY BIG BOY.

35:15.709 --> 35:17.542
YOU'RE VERY
CAPABLE.

35:17.542 --> 35:19.583
YOU'LL GET
THROUGH THIS FINE.

35:19.583 --> 35:21.291
[ Ding ]

35:23.500 --> 35:24.542
I HATE THE CELLO !

35:26.208 --> 35:28.166
DON'T.

35:32.333 --> 35:34.083
I KEEP WAITING FOR
"CANDID CAMERA" ...

35:34.083 --> 35:36.709
TO WALK
THROUGH THE DOOR.

35:36.709 --> 35:38.792
WHAT'D YOU CANCEL
FOR TONIGHT ?

35:38.792 --> 35:41.458
BOX SEATS AT SHEA.
YOU ?

35:41.458 --> 35:43.583
DINNER WITH
CHERYL.

35:45.875 --> 35:48.000
TWO MORE DAYS.

35:54.083 --> 35:56.250
WHERE'D YOU PUT
THE BABY POWDER ?

35:56.250 --> 35:57.750
I'LL GET IT.

35:57.750 --> 35:59.125
WHY'D YOU PUT
IT THERE ?

35:59.125 --> 36:01.417
WE'RE BATHING
HER IN HERE.

36:01.417 --> 36:03.250
IT'S JUST
DOWN THE HALL.

36:03.250 --> 36:05.083
WE DON'T BATHE
HER THERE.

36:05.083 --> 36:08.542
MAYBE WE SHOULD
START, GODDAMN IT !

36:08.542 --> 36:11.208
YOU'RE GOING TO
CLEAN THAT UP.

36:12.917 --> 36:15.458
[ Sigh ]

36:15.458 --> 36:17.125
WHAT TIME ARE THEY
GETTING HERE ?

36:17.125 --> 36:19.208
BEFORE NOON.
GOOD.

36:19.208 --> 36:20.542
I SEE MY EDITOR
ABOUT 1 PM.

36:22.000 --> 36:24.000
DID YOU MOVE
MY BLUEPRINTS ?

36:24.000 --> 36:25.959
I NEED THEM.

36:30.417 --> 36:32.208
SORRY.

36:41.166 --> 36:42.834
I THINK SHE
DID A DOODLE.

36:42.834 --> 36:46.166
YOUR TURN TO
CHANGE HER.

36:46.166 --> 36:48.792
I'LL GIVE YOU $1000
IF YOU'LL DO IT.

36:50.917 --> 36:53.000
[ Ding ]

37:02.750 --> 37:05.166
[ Doorbell ]

37:05.166 --> 37:07.250
COMING.

37:09.000 --> 37:10.500
DOES JACK HOLDEN
LIVE HERE ?

37:10.500 --> 37:13.083
SOMEONE ASKED US TO
PICK UP A PACKAGE.

37:13.083 --> 37:17.458
I LOVE THE WAY EVERYONE
CALLS IT A PACKAGE.

37:17.458 --> 37:20.208
TELL SYLVIA SHE'S GOT A LOT OF
NERVE DUMPING HER PROBLEMS --

37:21.333 --> 37:22.500
SYLVIA ?

37:22.500 --> 37:24.834
WE CONSIDERED
CALLING THE COPS.

37:24.834 --> 37:27.333
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

37:27.333 --> 37:29.125
... TOTALLY
DISRUPTED OUR LIVES.

37:29.125 --> 37:31.417
WE HAVEN'T
WORKED OR SLEPT.

37:31.417 --> 37:33.291
THERE'S BEEN SHIT
ALL OVER THE PLACE.

37:33.291 --> 37:34.166
SHIT ?

37:34.166 --> 37:35.375
WHAT ?

37:35.375 --> 37:36.792
THE PACKAGE BUSTED ?

37:36.792 --> 37:39.959
BUSTED ?
YOU COULD SAY THAT.

37:39.959 --> 37:41.208
DID YOU PUT
THE SHIT BACK ?

37:41.208 --> 37:44.208
NO, WE HAD IT
BRONZED FOR POSTERITY.

37:44.208 --> 37:45.417
MICHAEL.

37:49.208 --> 37:51.542
HER NEXT BOTTLE
IS IN 45 MINUTES.

37:51.542 --> 37:52.208
IT'S IN THE BASKET.

37:52.208 --> 37:55.000
IT'S A BABY.

37:55.000 --> 37:56.667
YOU'RE SHARP,
AREN'T YOU ?

37:56.667 --> 37:58.458
20 MINUTES AFTER EATING
SHE GETS TIRED.

37:58.458 --> 38:00.000
PUT HER TO BED.

38:00.000 --> 38:01.709
I'LL GET THE
POWDERED MILK.

38:01.709 --> 38:04.375
RIGHT,
POWDERED MILK.

38:06.875 --> 38:08.333
YEAH,
POWDERED MILK.

38:08.333 --> 38:12.417
WE'LL TAKE THE "POWDERED MILK"
AND GET OUT OF HERE.

38:20.083 --> 38:23.875
YOU WANT US
TO TAKE THE BABY ?

38:23.875 --> 38:26.291
THAT WAS THE
ARRANGEMENT.

38:28.583 --> 38:30.125
ARE YOU SURE ?

38:30.125 --> 38:31.583
YOU'RE DAMN
STRAIGHT.

38:33.083 --> 38:34.875
IF YOU SAY SO.

38:34.875 --> 38:36.250
LET'S GO.

38:36.250 --> 38:38.667
YOU WON'T FORGET
WHAT WE SAID ?

38:38.667 --> 38:39.709
NO.

38:39.709 --> 38:42.333
SHE LIKES TO BE
ROCKED TO SLEEP; GENTLY.

38:42.333 --> 38:47.917
GENTLY. ABSOLUTELY.
I CAN HANDLE IT.

38:47.917 --> 38:51.792
LEAVE YOUR PHONE NUMBER,
IN CASE YOU NEED ADVICE.

38:51.792 --> 38:54.458
I'LL CALL YOU.

39:06.417 --> 39:09.709
DO YOU HEAR THAT,
PETER ?
JUST LISTEN.

39:09.709 --> 39:11.959
ISN'T IT
WONDERFUL ?

39:11.959 --> 39:14.291
ISN'T WHAT
WONDERFUL ?

39:14.291 --> 39:15.959
QUIET.

39:15.959 --> 39:19.125
PEACE AND QUIET.

39:19.125 --> 39:20.792
SOMETHING SCREWY
IS GOING ON.

39:20.792 --> 39:22.625
I'VE GOT A
FUNNY FEELING.

39:22.625 --> 39:25.291
YOU'VE BEEN TENSE
THE LAST 5 DAYS.

39:25.291 --> 39:28.458
IT'S JUST YOUR
NERVES UNWINDING.

39:30.333 --> 39:32.542
MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.

39:45.208 --> 39:46.834
MICHAEL ...

39:50.792 --> 39:52.333
WHAT IS THIS ?

39:52.333 --> 39:53.583
A PACKAGE.

39:53.583 --> 39:55.583
WHEN DID IT
GET HERE ?

39:55.583 --> 39:58.333
SUNDAY.
MRS. HATHAWAY --

39:58.333 --> 40:00.125
GO TO THE WINDOW.
STOP THEM.

40:00.125 --> 40:02.041
I'LL CATCH UP
WITH THEM.

40:10.375 --> 40:12.375
YOU'RE BEAUTIFUL.

40:12.375 --> 40:14.500
WANT TO GO
FOR A RIDE ?

40:20.083 --> 40:21.709
HEY, UP HERE !

40:31.458 --> 40:33.291
WHERE WILL
I PUT HER ?

40:33.291 --> 40:35.041
ON YOUR LAP.

40:35.041 --> 40:37.250
WE NEED A
BABY CAR SEAT.

40:37.250 --> 40:38.959
PUT HER
IN THE TRUNK.

40:38.959 --> 40:42.250
YOU WANT TO RIDE
IN THE TRUNK ?

40:42.250 --> 40:43.625
WANT TO GO IN
THE TRUNK ?

40:47.208 --> 40:49.125
UMPH !

40:52.208 --> 40:53.834
OH, NO.

40:53.834 --> 40:55.625
OH, MY GOD !

40:57.417 --> 40:59.375
WANT TO TRY THIS ?
IT'S AN ADVENTURE.

41:01.417 --> 41:03.291
WHY DO I
LISTEN TO YOU ?

41:03.291 --> 41:06.166
IT'S ABSURD TO PUT
A BABY IN THE TRUNK.

41:07.875 --> 41:09.792
HEY !

41:09.792 --> 41:12.333
WONDERFUL.

41:12.333 --> 41:15.083
I GAVE YOU
THE WRONG PACKAGE.

41:15.083 --> 41:17.166
I MADE A
TERRIBLE MISTAKE.

41:17.166 --> 41:19.709
I GAVE YOU
THE WRONG PACKAGE.

41:19.709 --> 41:21.125
GIVE ME THE
BABY FIRST.

41:21.125 --> 41:22.375
GIVE ME
THE BABY !

41:22.375 --> 41:23.834
[ Baby Cries ]

41:23.834 --> 41:25.917
YOU'RE DISTURBING
THE BABY.

41:25.917 --> 41:26.917
GIVE ME
THE BABY.

41:26.917 --> 41:28.625
HEY, SATCH.

41:28.625 --> 41:31.417
THIS GUY'S AN ANIMAL.

41:31.417 --> 41:33.250
I KEEP HIM CHAINED
AND FEED HIM RAW MEAT.

41:33.250 --> 41:34.500
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

41:34.500 --> 41:36.125
IT'S ROY
AND TRIGGER.

41:36.125 --> 41:37.500
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

41:37.500 --> 41:38.917
NOTHING, OFFICER.

41:38.917 --> 41:42.291
YOU PUTTING THE
KID IN THE TRUNK ?

41:42.291 --> 41:45.583
NO, IT'S UNHEALTHY
AND IT'S ILLEGAL, ALSO.

41:45.583 --> 41:47.291
NO, HE'S NOT,
OFFICER.

41:47.291 --> 41:49.083
LET ME SEE YOUR
LICENSE AND REGISTRATION.

41:49.083 --> 41:50.333
WHY ?

41:50.333 --> 41:53.625
YOU'RE DOUBLE-PARKED,
WISE GUY !

41:53.625 --> 41:55.667
ALL RIGHT.
WAIT A MINUTE.

41:55.667 --> 41:59.125
BE GENTLE.

41:59.125 --> 42:02.208
I'LL BE RIGHT
WITH YOU.

42:06.166 --> 42:07.709
COME BACK HERE !
YOU, FREEZE !

42:11.417 --> 42:13.208
I HAVE NO
INTENTION OF MOVING.

42:13.208 --> 42:15.291
I'M NOT A CRIMINAL.

42:15.291 --> 42:17.583
I'M AN ARCHITECT
WITH A BABY, SEE ?

42:17.583 --> 42:20.125
LET ME SEE SOME I.D.

42:21.959 --> 42:23.375
I DON'T HAVE
ANY WITH ME.

42:23.375 --> 42:25.375
UP AGAINST THE
CAR, SPREAD 'EM.

42:25.375 --> 42:28.667
MY WALLET'S IN
MY APARTMENT.

42:28.667 --> 42:31.250
YOU CAN COME UP
WITH ME.

42:31.250 --> 42:32.792
I'LL SHOW YOU
SOME I.D.,

42:32.792 --> 42:36.208
BUT I WON'T SPREAD 'EM
BECAUSE I HAVE A BABY.

42:36.208 --> 42:38.667
LET'S GO,
ARCHITECT.

42:44.792 --> 42:46.417
HERE WE ARE.

42:46.417 --> 42:48.291
CAN I GET YOU
A CUP OF COFFEE ?

42:48.291 --> 42:50.125
NO THANKS.
I'LL JUST WAIT HERE.

42:50.125 --> 42:52.583
I'LL JUST
BE A SECOND.

42:54.417 --> 42:56.458
HERE WE GO.
I'M COMING.

42:56.458 --> 42:59.667
THE PACKAGE THOSE
GUYS CAME FOR ...

42:59.667 --> 43:00.875
IS FULL OF DRUGS.

43:00.875 --> 43:02.959
WHAT ?
DRUGS !!

43:02.959 --> 43:05.375
HERE.

43:05.375 --> 43:07.625
COMING.
DO SOMETHING WITH IT.

43:07.625 --> 43:09.917
LIKE WHAT ?
HIDE IT !

43:09.917 --> 43:13.083
I'M COMING.

43:14.709 --> 43:16.542
SORRY TO KEEP
YOU WAITING.

43:16.542 --> 43:19.333
REMOVE THAT FROM
THE COVER, PLEASE.

43:19.333 --> 43:21.583
SURE.
[ Baby Crying ]

43:21.583 --> 43:24.542
THANK YOU.

43:24.542 --> 43:28.583
SHH.
SHH.
SHH.

43:28.583 --> 43:31.291
SHHH.
SHHH.

43:31.291 --> 43:34.667
THANKS FOR COMING
UP, OFFICER.

43:34.667 --> 43:37.333
IF THERE'S ANYTHING ELSE
I CAN DO, LET ME KNOW.

43:37.333 --> 43:39.041
I WAS JUST
DOING MY JOB.

43:39.041 --> 43:40.542
[ Ding ]

43:43.083 --> 43:46.500
I'M DETECTIVE SERGEANT
MELKOWITZ, NARCOTICS.

43:46.500 --> 43:49.375
OFFICER, YOU CAN
SADDLE UP NOW.

43:49.375 --> 43:51.417
I'LL HANDLE THIS.

43:58.500 --> 43:59.625
AREN'T YOU GOING
TO ASK ME IN ?

44:10.417 --> 44:13.125
CAN I GET YOU A CUP
OF COFFEE; WATER, BEER ?

44:13.125 --> 44:14.750
THANKS,
I'M FINE.

44:16.500 --> 44:20.083
YOU DON'T MIND ME
ASKING A FEW QUESTIONS ?

44:20.083 --> 44:21.250
NO, NOT AT ALL.

44:21.250 --> 44:23.458
IS THAT YOUR BABY
I SAW DOWNSTAIRS ?

44:23.458 --> 44:26.792
NO, IT'S MY
ROOMMATE JACK'S.

44:26.792 --> 44:29.458
WHO WERE THOSE 2 MEN
YOU WERE TALKING TO ?

44:29.458 --> 44:32.125
FRIENDS ...
OF THE MOTHER'S.

44:32.125 --> 44:34.458
THEY WERE GOING TO
TAKE HER FOR A RIDE.

44:34.458 --> 44:36.667
THE BABY,
NOT THE MOTHER.

44:36.667 --> 44:38.750
THEY COULDN'T
BECAUSE THE CAR ...

44:38.750 --> 44:41.291
HAD NO
BABY SEAT.

44:41.291 --> 44:43.709
MIND IF I HAVE A
LOOK AT THAT BABY ?

44:43.709 --> 44:46.125
I JUST LOVE
LITTLE BABIES.

44:46.125 --> 44:48.417
SHE'S SLEEPING.

44:48.417 --> 44:50.000
[ Baby Babbles ]

44:50.000 --> 44:51.583
SOUNDS LIKE
SHE'S AWAKE.

44:51.583 --> 44:53.333
MIND IF I
SEE HER ?

44:53.333 --> 44:56.125
SHE DOESN'T
LIKE STRANGERS.

44:56.125 --> 44:57.417
SHE MAY NOT BE DECENT.

44:57.417 --> 44:59.542
I DON'T THINK
SHE'LL MIND.

45:02.333 --> 45:06.625
THERE SHE IS,
AND SHE'S GOT A FRIEND.

45:06.625 --> 45:09.667
THIS IS MY
OTHER ROOMMATE.

45:09.667 --> 45:12.125
DETECTIVE MELKOWITZ;
MICHAEL KELLAM.

45:12.125 --> 45:13.542
HELLO.

45:13.542 --> 45:15.917
WHAT A CUTIE.

45:15.917 --> 45:18.166
MIND IF I HOLD HER ?
I JUST LOVE KIDS.

45:18.166 --> 45:20.500
I'D RATHER NOT.

45:20.500 --> 45:21.792
GO AHEAD.
IT WON'T HURT.

45:21.792 --> 45:25.333
YOU KNOW HOW SHE
IS AROUND PEOPLE.

45:25.333 --> 45:27.333
LET HIM
HOLD HER.

45:27.333 --> 45:28.542
HE WON'T
HURT HER.

45:28.542 --> 45:30.542
HE'S A
POLICE OFFICER.

45:30.542 --> 45:32.750
ALL RIGHT.

45:34.000 --> 45:37.125
OHHH.

45:37.125 --> 45:38.834
[ Chuckle ]

45:42.875 --> 45:44.583
YOU'RE A HEAVY LITTLE
GIRL, AREN'T YOU ?

45:44.583 --> 45:47.667
[ Baby Coos ]

45:47.667 --> 45:49.667
YES.
YES.
YES.

45:49.667 --> 45:51.083
SHE REALLY IS
HEAVY, ISN'T SHE ?

45:51.083 --> 45:52.625
SHE'S A GOOD EATER.

45:52.625 --> 45:55.291
GOOD.
IT MEANS SHE WON'T
GROW UP TO BE NERVOUS.

45:56.834 --> 46:03.208
YOU'VE GOT NOTHING TO
BE NERVOUS ABOUT, SWEETIE.

46:03.208 --> 46:05.125
SHE'S READY
FOR A CHANGE.

46:05.125 --> 46:07.250
OH !

46:07.250 --> 46:09.583
YOU KNOW BABIES;
EAT, SLEEP, AND POOP.

46:09.583 --> 46:11.250
- I'LL CHANGE HER.
- GOOD IDEA.

46:12.375 --> 46:15.000
WHAT A CUTE
LITTLE BABY.

46:15.000 --> 46:17.250
DO YOU KNOW WHERE
HER FATHER IS ?

46:17.250 --> 46:21.208
NO.
HE'S ON LOCATION
DOING A TV MOVIE,

46:21.208 --> 46:23.583
BUT I HAVE
NO IDEA WHERE.

46:23.583 --> 46:26.208
DO YOU KNOW
THIS GUY ?

46:29.041 --> 46:31.375
NOT VERY WELL.
HE'S A FRIEND OF JACK'S.

46:31.375 --> 46:33.792
I DON'T REMEMBER
HIS NAME.

46:33.792 --> 46:37.208
HE'S PAUL MILNER.
HE DIRECTS TV COMMERCIALS.

46:37.208 --> 46:39.750
ON THE SIDE, HE DABBLES
IN HEROIN SMUGGLING.

46:42.583 --> 46:44.667
REALLY ?

46:44.667 --> 46:47.083
YEAH.

46:47.083 --> 46:49.709
I DON'T KNOW HIM.

46:49.709 --> 46:52.583
I'D APPRECIATE THAT
GLASS OF WATER NOW.

46:52.583 --> 46:55.500
OF COURSE.
NO PROBLEM.

46:55.500 --> 46:57.667
THANK YOU.

46:58.750 --> 47:01.083
I'VE GOT IT.

47:08.458 --> 47:12.750
[ Phone Rings ]

47:12.750 --> 47:15.000
[ Answering Machine ] HI, THIS
IS PETER, MICHAEL, AND JACK.

47:15.000 --> 47:17.125
WE'RE OUT PLAYING.

47:17.125 --> 47:18.125
SHIT !

47:19.458 --> 47:22.500
WHOEVER IT IS, I'M HERE.

47:22.500 --> 47:24.250
PETER ?
JACK.

47:24.250 --> 47:25.667
HOW ARE YOU ?

47:25.667 --> 47:28.792
I GOT A MESSAGE THAT
YOU WERE TRYING TO REACH ME.

47:28.792 --> 47:32.000
MICHAEL AND I REALLY
HAVE TO TALK TO YOU,

47:32.000 --> 47:34.667
BUT YOU CALLED US
AT A BAD TIME.

47:34.667 --> 47:36.083
WE'LL CALL BACK LATER.

47:36.083 --> 47:38.625
I'M CALLING FROM TURKEY.

47:38.625 --> 47:40.917
IT TOOK ME AN
HOUR TO GET THROUGH.

47:40.917 --> 47:43.583
IT'S NOT AN EASY
PLACE TO PHONE FROM.

47:43.583 --> 47:45.500
THIS PLACE
IS AMAZING.

47:45.500 --> 47:48.709
YOU WILL NOT BELIEVE
THE STUFF I BOUGHT FOR YOU.

47:48.709 --> 47:51.291
THIS SHIT IS
SO CHEAP HERE.

47:51.291 --> 47:55.083
I PROBABLY BOUGHT TOO MUCH,
BUT I CAN ALWAYS SMUGGLE IT IN.

47:55.083 --> 47:57.333
HA, HA.
I WAS KIDDING.

47:57.333 --> 48:01.041
THANKS FOR CALLING.
WE'LL
SEE YOU WHEN YOU GET BACK.

48:06.667 --> 48:08.000
OH !

48:10.166 --> 48:12.166
I GOTTA GET HIM
A GLASS OF WATER,

48:12.166 --> 48:15.917
SO HIS MOUTH ISN'T DRY
WHEN HE READS ME MY RIGHTS.

48:20.625 --> 48:23.041
HERE YOU ARE,
SERGEANT.

48:34.333 --> 48:35.834
GOOD-BYE.

48:35.834 --> 48:38.041
NICE TALKING
TO YOU.

48:38.041 --> 48:40.208
IT WAS VERY
ILLUMINATING.

48:44.792 --> 48:47.208
HE HEARD THE
PHONE CALL.
WE'RE DEAD.

48:47.208 --> 48:49.834
YOU THINK
JACK'S INVOLVED ?
I DON'T KNOW.

48:49.834 --> 48:52.125
WE GOTTA TALK
TO PAUL MILNER.

48:52.125 --> 48:53.166
WHY ?

48:53.166 --> 48:55.375
HE IS  INVOLVED.

48:57.875 --> 49:00.041
COULDN'T YOU THINK OF SOMEWHERE
BETTER TO HIDE THE DRUGS ?

49:00.041 --> 49:02.542
IT WAS PERFECT UNTIL YOU
INSISTED THAT HE HOLD THE BABY.

49:02.542 --> 49:05.667
I'M SORRY.
WHERE'D YOU PUT 'EM NOW ?

49:05.667 --> 49:07.500
IN THE GARBAGE PAIL
UNDER THE DIRTY DIAPERS.

49:07.500 --> 49:09.709
NOBODY'S GONNA
LOOK FOR IT THERE.

49:09.709 --> 49:11.500
YOU REALIZE WE'RE IN
TROUBLE WITH THIS COP ?

49:11.500 --> 49:14.917
YOU REALIZE THAT NO ONE'S
COMING BACK FOR THIS KID ?

49:14.917 --> 49:18.083
JESUS, YOU'RE RIGHT.

49:18.083 --> 49:20.417
WE'RE STUCK WITH HER
'TIL JACK GETS BACK.

49:20.417 --> 49:23.166
THIS IS DISCONNECTED.

49:23.959 --> 49:25.458
OH, I'M LATE.

49:25.458 --> 49:26.709
WAIT A MINUTE.
SO AM I.

49:26.709 --> 49:29.166
OH, DAMN IT.

49:29.166 --> 49:30.750
MR. KELLAM ?

49:31.709 --> 49:33.667
MR. MITCHELL ?

49:36.417 --> 49:37.834
HELLO,
MRS. HATHAWAY.

49:37.834 --> 49:40.500
IT SEEMS
THAT A HORSE ...

49:40.500 --> 49:42.750
HAS BEFOULED
THE FRONT WALK.

49:42.750 --> 49:44.959
DO YOU KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT IT ?

49:46.083 --> 49:48.166
MRS. HATHAWAY,
HOW NICE TO SEE YOU.

49:48.166 --> 49:50.083
REALLY NICE
TO SEE YOU.

49:50.083 --> 49:51.959
[ Chuckling ] OH.

49:51.959 --> 49:54.667
SHE CAN SIT
'TIL 5 P.M.
I'LL HURRY.

49:54.667 --> 49:56.959
ME, TOO.
I'M WORRIED.

50:00.917 --> 50:03.542
I GOT THE ONE
WITH THE MOUSTACHE.

50:03.542 --> 50:06.709
I'LL TELL MELKOWITZ
WE'RE MOVING.

50:19.542 --> 50:21.125
THERE.

50:30.542 --> 50:32.792
THERE YOU
GO, PAL.

50:32.792 --> 50:34.208
WHAT CAN
I DO FOR YA ?

50:34.208 --> 50:37.291
I'D LIKE "SPORTS ILLUSTRATED",
"POPULAR SCIENCE,"

50:37.291 --> 50:40.792
SOME GUM AND
THAT GIRAFFE UP THERE.

50:40.792 --> 50:42.834
WHICH ONE'S
THE GIRAFFE ?

50:42.834 --> 50:44.542
THE RUBBER ONE.

50:44.542 --> 50:47.375
THAT'S NOT A GIRAFFE,
THAT'S A DINOSAUR.

50:47.375 --> 50:48.542
WHATEVER.

50:48.542 --> 50:50.500
THE ONE WITH
THE POLKA DOTS ?

50:50.500 --> 50:53.917
YEAH, THAT'S IT.
THAT'S A DINOSAUR,
NOT A GIRAFFE.

50:53.917 --> 50:56.750
I DON'T CARE.
JUST GIMME THE DAMN THING.

50:59.667 --> 51:02.250
WHAT ABOUT
YOUR CHANGE ?
NEVER MIND.

51:27.291 --> 51:29.250
MRS. HATHAWAY,
I'M HOME.

51:29.250 --> 51:31.959
[ Muffled Voice ]

51:33.375 --> 51:35.375
MRS. HATHAWAY !

51:35.375 --> 51:37.417
MRS. HATHAWAY,
WHERE'S MARY ?
I DON'T KNOW.

51:41.542 --> 51:43.041
MARY ?

51:43.041 --> 51:45.250
OH. MY GOD.

51:46.709 --> 51:47.542
MARY !

51:48.500 --> 51:49.792
MARY !

51:50.959 --> 51:51.959
MARY !

51:55.542 --> 51:56.041
MARY !

51:58.208 --> 52:00.375
MARY !

52:02.458 --> 52:03.542
MARY !

52:08.333 --> 52:09.792
MARY !

52:09.792 --> 52:12.834
[ Baby Cries ]

52:14.959 --> 52:23.083
[ Baby Cries ]

52:24.917 --> 52:28.250
[ Sighs ]
THANK GOD.

52:31.458 --> 52:33.333
THANK GOD.

52:34.333 --> 52:36.458
NO, EVERYTHING'S
FINE, DARLING.

52:36.458 --> 52:37.917
EVERYTHING'S FINE.

52:37.917 --> 52:39.291
DON'T YOU WORRY.

52:42.500 --> 52:45.083
NOBODY'S GONNA
HURT YOU.

52:45.083 --> 52:45.834
NO, IT'S OKAY.

52:45.834 --> 52:47.583
PETER !

52:47.583 --> 52:48.959
PETER !

52:50.792 --> 52:52.125
SHE'S OKAY.

52:52.125 --> 52:53.041
SHE'S NOT HURT.

52:55.667 --> 52:57.875
HOW ARE YOU ?

52:57.875 --> 53:01.375
I'M FINE, JUST FINE.

53:01.375 --> 53:04.500
DID YOU SEE WHAT THOSE BASTARDS
DID TO MY VIDEOTAPES ?

53:04.500 --> 53:06.125
WE GOT A MESSAGE.

53:06.750 --> 53:09.625
WHAT'D IT SAY ?

53:11.458 --> 53:13.250
"NEXT TIME,
WE'LL TAKE THE BABY."

53:13.250 --> 53:16.709
IT'S OKAY.
IT'S OKAY.

53:16.709 --> 53:18.125
MR. KELLAM ?

53:19.750 --> 53:23.083
MR. MITCHELL ?

53:23.083 --> 53:26.166
"THE CHAMP CAUGHT SMITH WITH
A SAVAGE LEFT HOOK ...

53:26.166 --> 53:30.458
"THAT SENT THE CHALLENGER
CRASHING INTO THE ROPES.

53:30.458 --> 53:33.417
"SMITH, HIS LEFT EYE SWOLLEN,

53:33.417 --> 53:37.875
"AND THE CUT ABOVE HIS RIGHT
EYE NOW MUCH MORE BLOODY,

53:37.875 --> 53:41.792
COUNTERED WITH A BARRAGE
OF VICIOUS BODY BLOWS."

53:41.792 --> 53:43.250
WHAT ARE YOU
READING HER ?

53:43.250 --> 53:45.917
IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT I READ,

53:45.917 --> 53:48.875
IT'S THE TONE YOU USE.

53:48.875 --> 53:50.917
SHE DOESN'T UNDERSTAND
THE WORDS, ANYWAY.

53:50.917 --> 53:52.500
NOW, WHERE WERE WE ?

53:52.500 --> 53:59.250
"THE CHAMP BEGAN THE 5th ROUND
LIKE A MAN POSSESSED,

53:59.250 --> 54:03.792
"GOING STRAIGHT FOR HIS
OPPONENT'S BODY ...

54:03.792 --> 54:07.000
WITH FEROCIOUS ENERGY."

54:16.709 --> 54:19.542
[ Baby Gurgles ]

54:21.667 --> 54:23.542
[ Baby Coos ]

54:32.208 --> 54:34.583
[ Toy Squeaks ]

54:36.083 --> 54:39.458
[ Baby Laughs ]

55:15.834 --> 55:17.917
[ Click ]

55:31.750 --> 55:34.834
[ Footsteps ]

55:48.291 --> 55:49.667
OOOHHH !

55:51.834 --> 55:53.500
[ Grunt ]

55:57.792 --> 55:58.750
BANG !!!

55:58.750 --> 56:01.000
[ Grunts ]

56:01.000 --> 56:03.458
JEEZ !
MY FACE !
WATCH OUT FOR MY FACE !

56:03.458 --> 56:05.792
PETER !
IT'S ME, JACK !
JACK !

56:05.792 --> 56:06.834
JESUS, JACK !

56:06.834 --> 56:08.959
JACK !
NO, WAIT.

56:08.959 --> 56:10.583
GET HIM OFF ME.
YOU IRRESPONSIBLE --

56:10.583 --> 56:12.458
WHAT IS IT WITH YOU GUYS !

56:12.458 --> 56:14.041
WE SHOULD BE ASKING YOU
THAT QUESTION.

56:14.041 --> 56:15.542
WHAT'D I DO ?

56:15.542 --> 56:17.291
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOING
BACK SO SOON ANYWAY ?

56:17.291 --> 56:21.041
- MY PART GOT CUT, OKAY ?
- GOOD !

56:21.041 --> 56:22.041
WHAT IS WITH HIM ?

56:22.041 --> 56:24.333
LOOK AT THIS PLACE.

56:24.333 --> 56:27.166
WHAT THE HELL IS
GOING ON AROUND HERE ?

56:27.166 --> 56:29.917
[ Baby Starts Crying ]

56:29.917 --> 56:32.208
AW, SHIT !

56:32.208 --> 56:34.458
WHAT WAS THAT ?
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE ...

56:34.458 --> 56:37.375
'TIL YOU TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON.
WE'LL BE GLAD TO.

56:37.375 --> 56:39.417
THAT REALLY HURT,
PETER.
OW, OW, OW.

56:39.417 --> 56:42.417
SUNDAY MORNING,
I COME BACK FROM JOGGING ...

56:42.417 --> 56:46.458
TO FIND THIS BASKET,
WITH THIS BABY  IN IT ...

56:46.458 --> 56:47.834
WAITING IN THE VESTIBULE.

56:47.834 --> 56:49.583
WHA --, WHAT ?

56:49.583 --> 56:52.583
INSIDE IS A NOTE FROM SYLVIA
SAYING THE BABY WAS YOURS,

56:52.583 --> 56:54.667
AND SHE WAS LEAVING IT HERE
FOR YOU TO DEAL WITH.

56:54.667 --> 56:56.667
MINE ?

56:56.667 --> 56:58.959
THEN, ALONG COMES ANOTHER
PACKAGE WITH YOUR NAME ON IT.

56:58.959 --> 57:01.667
ONLY THIS TIME,
THE PACKAGE HAS HEROIN IN IT,

57:01.667 --> 57:06.291
AND THE NARCOTICS SQUAD, CAMPED
DOWNSTAIRS, KNOWS ALL ABOUT IT.
THE COPS ?

57:06.291 --> 57:08.250
I DON'T BELIEVE THIS.

57:08.250 --> 57:10.583
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING ABOUT
ANY DRUGS OR ANY POLICE.

57:10.583 --> 57:12.458
I THOUGHT I WAS JUST
DOING A FAVOR FOR PAUL.

57:12.458 --> 57:14.291
I DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT WAS IN THAT PACKAGE.

57:14.291 --> 57:16.667
I CERTAINLY DON'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT THAT BABY.

57:16.667 --> 57:21.542
SOMEBODY DROPS A BABY OFF,
AND YOU ASSUME HE'S MINE ?

57:23.000 --> 57:25.583
THE CHILD DOESN'T LOOK
ANYTHING LIKE ME.

57:25.583 --> 57:27.166
[ Baby Coos ]

57:27.166 --> 57:28.750
I'M BIGGER ...

57:28.750 --> 57:30.458
AND I HAVE
MORE HAIR.

57:30.458 --> 57:32.333
"DEAR JACK,
HERE'S OUR BABY.

57:32.333 --> 57:35.250
I CAN'T HANDLE THIS NOW.
I
DON'T KNOW WHERE ELSE TO TURN."

57:36.750 --> 57:38.208
"SYLVIA."

57:39.792 --> 57:41.083
OH, MY GOD !

57:41.083 --> 57:44.583
STRATFORD.
A YEAR
AND A HALF AGO --

57:46.792 --> 57:48.208
I WAS DOING
"TAMING OF THE SHREW."

57:48.208 --> 57:49.583
SHE WAS THE SHREW.

57:49.583 --> 57:51.959
I DID SOME OF MY
BEST WORK IN THAT.

57:53.166 --> 57:54.583
I GOT GREAT REVIEWS.

57:54.583 --> 57:56.875
JACK, YOU'RE
SUCH A JERK.

57:56.875 --> 57:59.083
YOU'RE ALWAYS THINKING ABOUT
YOURSELF.
I WANT TO KILL YOU.

57:59.083 --> 58:01.625
MICHAEL,
WE WON'T HAVE TO.

58:01.625 --> 58:06.667
JACK, I WOULD LIKE TO INTRODUCE
YOU TO YOUR DAUGHTER, MARY.

58:10.083 --> 58:12.792
WAIT A MINUTE.
YOU CAN'T
BE SURE THIS IS MY KID.

58:12.792 --> 58:15.333
UH, UH --

58:15.333 --> 58:16.917
WHAT THE HELL AM I
SUPPOSED TO DO WITH IT ?

58:16.917 --> 58:21.417
WE'VE PUT OUR LIVES ON HOLD,
JACK, TAKING CARE OF THIS KID.

58:21.417 --> 58:24.667
NOW, IT'S YOUR TURN.

58:26.250 --> 58:28.792
OKAY, ALL RIGHT.
FINE.

58:31.291 --> 58:33.083
UNTIL I STRAIGHTEN
THIS MESS OUT,

58:33.083 --> 58:35.667
I'LL TAKE CARE OF HER.

58:35.667 --> 58:42.125
WHY NOT ?
I'M AN ACTOR.
I CAN DO A FATHER.

58:42.125 --> 58:46.834
YEAH.
WHAT CAN
BE SO DIFFICULT ?

58:46.834 --> 58:49.959
GOOD NIGHT,
JACK.
GOOD NIGHT.

58:49.959 --> 58:52.709
OH, DOWN WE GO.
[ Baby Starts Crying ]

58:52.709 --> 58:55.625
WAIT A MINUTE !
WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH HER ?

58:55.625 --> 58:57.792
GOOD NIGHT, JACK.
GOOD NIGHT, JACK.

59:05.375 --> 59:07.583
HOLD STILL,
KID.
JEEZ.

59:07.583 --> 59:09.917
HOW DO YOU PUT ON THESE
GODDAMN THINGS, ANYWAY ?

59:09.917 --> 59:14.083
FIGURE IT OUT FOR
YOURSELF, DICKHEAD.
NICE SHOT.

59:14.083 --> 59:15.709
LOOK AT
THAT STUFF !

59:15.709 --> 59:18.083
OH, MY GOD.
WHAT ARE YOU
GUYS FEEDING HER, HUH ?

59:18.083 --> 59:21.166
OH, NO, NOT ON THE SILK SHEETS !
NOT ON THE SILK SHEETS !

59:21.166 --> 59:24.166
MAYBE I SHOULD SHOW HIM
HOW TO PUT ON THE DIAPER.

59:24.166 --> 59:27.208
OH, NO.
I DON'T BELIEVE
THIS. WHY ME ?
PLEASE !

59:27.208 --> 59:29.041
COME ON,
BABY !

59:29.041 --> 59:33.166
NOPE.
LET'S GIVE HIM
ANOTHER HALF HOUR.

59:33.166 --> 59:35.667
LET HIM
SUFFER.

59:38.000 --> 59:40.959
[ Baby Gurgles ]
YES, YES.
I'M TRYING
TO REACH PAUL MILNER.

59:40.959 --> 59:44.000
NO, HE WAS SUPPOSED TO BE IN SAN
FRANCISCO, BUT I CAN'T FIND HIM.

59:44.000 --> 59:47.917
PLEASE TELL HIM TO CALL JACK
HOLDEN AS SOON AS HE GETS IN.

59:47.917 --> 59:49.875
IS THIS
URGENT ?

59:49.875 --> 59:51.959
YEAH, "URGENT'S"
AN UNDERSTATEMENT ...

59:51.959 --> 59:54.583
LADY.

59:56.458 --> 59:58.667
I DON'T KNOW WHY I BOTHER
TO GIVE YOU THIS.

59:58.667 --> 01:00:00.709
IT JUST GOES
RIGHT THROUGH YOU.

01:00:00.709 --> 01:00:02.500
DID YOU GET HOLD
OF YOUR FRIEND ?

01:00:02.500 --> 01:00:05.041
NO.
DON'T FORGET TO
BOLT THE DOOR.

01:00:05.041 --> 01:00:06.875
I WON'T.

01:00:06.875 --> 01:00:09.709
REMEMBER, THERE'S $250,000 IN
HEROIN IN THAT DIAPER PAIL.

01:00:09.709 --> 01:00:11.583
THE BABY WIPES
ARE IN THE CABINET.

01:00:11.583 --> 01:00:14.166
RIGHT.
HEROIN'S
IN THE DIAPER PAIL,

01:00:14.166 --> 01:00:17.417
BABY WIPES ARE IN THE CABINET.
WHERE ELSE WOULD THEY BE ?

01:00:17.417 --> 01:00:20.583
I CAN'T
BELIEVE THIS.

01:00:20.583 --> 01:00:23.583
YOU'RE KIDDING ME ?
THIRTY-TWO
BENNINGTONS IN THE LONDON AREA ?

01:00:23.583 --> 01:00:26.583
YES,
SIR.

01:00:26.583 --> 01:00:29.458
UH, I'LL GET BACK
TO YOU.
I, I --

01:00:29.458 --> 01:00:32.083
OH, BOY.

01:00:32.083 --> 01:00:34.750
[ Baby Cries ]

01:00:34.750 --> 01:00:38.834
I KNOW, I KNOW.
YES, YES, YES.
SSHH.

01:00:38.834 --> 01:00:40.750
[ Cries Louder ]

01:00:42.792 --> 01:00:46.083
OH, GOD.
YEAH, YEAH.

01:00:47.417 --> 01:00:50.750
WELL, WE TRIED YOUR MOMMY.
MAYBE I SHOULD, UH,

01:00:50.750 --> 01:00:53.667
MAYBE I SHOULD
TRY MINE, HUH ?

01:00:53.667 --> 01:00:55.750
[ Crying Stops ]

01:00:58.083 --> 01:01:00.458
YEAH.

01:01:02.667 --> 01:01:04.709
MOM !

01:01:04.709 --> 01:01:06.750
WELL, WHERE
IS SHE ?

01:01:06.750 --> 01:01:10.083
OH, MOM.
WAIT 'TIL YOU SEE HER.
YOU WON'T BELIEVE THIS.

01:01:10.083 --> 01:01:12.917
SHE IS SO BEAUTIFUL.
SHE LOOKS JUST LIKE YOU.

01:01:12.917 --> 01:01:15.333
YOU KNOW, YOU
BOYS LIVE LIKE PIGS.

01:01:15.333 --> 01:01:17.417
OH, MOM.

01:01:17.417 --> 01:01:19.750
LOOK, THERE.
ISN'T SHE BEAUTIFUL ?

01:01:19.750 --> 01:01:23.208
THERE SHE IS !
LOOK AT THAT LITTLE BABY !

01:01:23.208 --> 01:01:26.250
WILL YOU COME TO ME ?
I'M GONNA PICK YOU RIGHT UP.

01:01:26.250 --> 01:01:28.625
YES, I'M GONNA
PICK YOU RIGHT UP.

01:01:28.625 --> 01:01:30.834
OH, I'M IN AWE.
I MEAN, LOOK AT YOU;

01:01:30.834 --> 01:01:32.625
YOU PICK HER
UP LIKE A PRO.

01:01:32.625 --> 01:01:34.959
I PICK HER UP
LIKE A GRANDMOTHER.

01:01:34.959 --> 01:01:37.250
[ Baby Laughs ]
THAT'S CALLED
EXPERIENCE.

01:01:37.250 --> 01:01:38.792
DARLING,
LET'S SEE YOU.

01:01:38.792 --> 01:01:42.083
SHE'S SO LOVELY.
WHAT'S HER NAME ?
MARY.

01:01:42.083 --> 01:01:43.709
MARY !
[ Baby Laughs ]

01:01:43.709 --> 01:01:46.917
WELL, MARY !

01:01:46.917 --> 01:01:49.875
LOOK AT THE WAY
SHE'S LOOKING AT ME.

01:01:49.875 --> 01:01:52.875
FOR A MOMENT, THERE,
I HAD HER LAUGHING.

01:01:52.875 --> 01:01:56.083
YEAH, JUST
LIKE ME, HUH ?

01:01:56.083 --> 01:01:58.917
DON'T RUIN THIS
FOR ME, JACK.

01:01:58.917 --> 01:02:01.834
OH, SHE
ADORES YOU.

01:02:01.834 --> 01:02:04.625
SHE KNOWS THAT
YOU'RE HER GRANDMOTHER.

01:02:04.625 --> 01:02:07.583
IT'S LIKE A BIOLOGICAL THING,
AN INSTANT CONNECTION.

01:02:07.583 --> 01:02:12.125
CUT THE CRAP, JACK.
WHAT DO YOU WANT ?

01:02:12.125 --> 01:02:15.542
MOM, I CAN'T TAKE
CARE OF HER.

01:02:15.542 --> 01:02:17.667
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO.

01:02:17.667 --> 01:02:20.500
I WAS HOPING THAT YOU COULD
TAKE HER FOR A LITTLE WHILE,

01:02:20.500 --> 01:02:22.834
NOT FOREVER.
YOU KNOW,
UNTIL SHE'S READY TO VOTE ?

01:02:22.834 --> 01:02:26.500
OH, I WOULD
LOVE TO.

01:02:26.500 --> 01:02:29.500
DO YOU KNOW, JACK, SOME PEOPLE
LIVE ALL THEIR LIVES ...

01:02:29.500 --> 01:02:34.208
WITHOUT HAVING ANYTHING THIS
WONDERFUL TO SHOW FOR IT ?

01:02:34.208 --> 01:02:36.208
I KNOW,
MOM.

01:02:36.208 --> 01:02:39.250
I'M GOING TO DO THE MOST
WONDERFUL THING FOR YOU;

01:02:39.250 --> 01:02:41.375
ABSOLUTELY
NOTHING.

01:02:41.375 --> 01:02:45.000
WHY ?

01:02:45.000 --> 01:02:49.041
JACK, YOU'VE ALWAYS RUN
AWAY FROM RESPONSIBILITY.

01:02:49.041 --> 01:02:52.208
NOW, YOU HAVE TO
TURN AND FACE IT.

01:02:54.458 --> 01:02:58.000
MOM ...
I'M A SCREW-UP.

01:02:58.000 --> 01:03:00.917
YOU WERE  A SCREW-UP.
NOW, YOU'RE A FATHER,

01:03:00.917 --> 01:03:05.917
AND YOU'LL
BE A FINE ONE.

01:03:05.917 --> 01:03:07.125
THINK SO ?

01:03:07.125 --> 01:03:08.750
I KNOW IT.

01:03:11.542 --> 01:03:15.917
YOUR FATHER, GOD REST
HIS SOUL, HE WAS A SCREW-UP,

01:03:15.917 --> 01:03:19.250
AND HE TURNED
OUT JUST FINE.

01:03:19.250 --> 01:03:20.917
REALLY ?

01:03:20.917 --> 01:03:23.500
DON'T YOU
REMEMBER ?
YEAH,
I GUESS

01:03:23.500 --> 01:03:26.709
NOW, GIVE
ME A KISS.

01:03:26.709 --> 01:03:30.250
MARY, GIVE
ME A KISS.

01:03:30.250 --> 01:03:34.291
NOW, YOU AND
YOUR FRIENDS ...

01:03:34.291 --> 01:03:36.041
CLEAN THIS
PLACE UP.

01:03:36.041 --> 01:03:39.458
IF NOT FOR YOURSELVES,
DO IT FOR MY GRANDDAUGHTER.

01:03:39.458 --> 01:03:41.750
WE WILL,
WE WILL.

01:03:41.750 --> 01:03:44.667
BYE.
THANKS
ANYWAY, MOM.

01:03:46.166 --> 01:03:50.208
WELL, LOOKS LIKE IT'S
JUST YOU AND ME NOW, HUH ?

01:03:50.208 --> 01:03:52.875
[ Baby Babbles ]
WHAT ?

01:03:52.875 --> 01:03:56.333
OH, JACK ?
THERE'S 4
BOTTLES PREPARED ALREADY,

01:03:56.333 --> 01:04:00.166
SO YOU SHOULD BE FINE
UNTIL TOMORROW MORNING.

01:04:00.166 --> 01:04:03.125
IF HER BOTTOM GETS RED,
GIVE HER A BOTTLE OF WATER.

01:04:03.125 --> 01:04:05.542
IN ABOUT 3 HOURS ...
WHITE AS MARBLE.

01:04:05.542 --> 01:04:07.792
WE'LL BE IN SEATS
D-11 THROUGH 14.

01:04:07.792 --> 01:04:11.000
IF THERE'S A PROBLEM,
THE USHER WILL GET US.

01:04:11.000 --> 01:04:14.458
OH, HERE'S
THE NUMBER.

01:04:14.458 --> 01:04:17.250
WAIT A MINUTE.
ARE YOU LEAVING RIGHT NOW ?

01:04:17.250 --> 01:04:19.291
WHEN ARE YOU
COMING BACK ?

01:04:19.291 --> 01:04:20.709
AROUND
MIDNIGHT.

01:04:20.709 --> 01:04:22.625
DON'T WORRY
ABOUT US.

01:04:22.625 --> 01:04:24.959
IS THIS
A FOUR ?
YEAH.

01:04:26.291 --> 01:04:30.041
[ Baby Squeals ]
IT'S GOOD TO HAVE.

01:04:31.959 --> 01:04:34.625
SO, UH, WHAT DO
YOU WANT TO DO ?

01:04:38.417 --> 01:04:43.000
[ Indistinct Chatter ]

01:04:43.000 --> 01:04:46.250
THIS SHOW'S BEEN RUNNING
LONGER THAN MARY'S BEEN ALIVE.

01:04:46.250 --> 01:04:48.917
PETER, WE AGREED NOT TO MENTION
HER NAME TONIGHT, RIGHT ?

01:04:48.917 --> 01:04:50.875
RIGHT.
MY MISTAKE.

01:04:50.875 --> 01:04:52.834
WHO DID YOU GUYS CON
INTO SITTING FOR YOU ?

01:04:52.834 --> 01:04:53.625
JACK.

01:04:53.625 --> 01:04:55.667
JACK ?
DADDY ?

01:04:55.667 --> 01:04:58.166
WOOO --

01:05:06.750 --> 01:05:08.667
ARE YOU
HUNGRY ?

01:05:08.667 --> 01:05:10.667
WELL, WE'RE
IN LUCK HERE.

01:05:10.667 --> 01:05:14.166
[ Mock French Accent ]
TONIGHT, THE CHEF HAS ...

01:05:14.166 --> 01:05:16.417
COOKED UP SOMETHING
VERY SPECIAL FOR YOU.

01:05:16.417 --> 01:05:20.166
HE HAS TAKEN THE
JUICE OF ONE COW,

01:05:20.166 --> 01:05:23.709
AND SAUTEED IT
WITH A FINE SAUCE.

01:05:23.709 --> 01:05:27.000
IT IS PRESENTED,
SURROUNDED BY A BOTTLE,

01:05:27.000 --> 01:05:30.625
AND TOPPED OFF WITH A
DELICIOUS RUBBER NIPPLE, EH ?

01:05:30.625 --> 01:05:32.166
[ Continues Gurgling ]

01:05:32.166 --> 01:05:35.375
EXCELLENT CHOICE !
YES, YES, HERE WE GO.

01:05:35.375 --> 01:05:38.917
AH, YES.

01:05:38.917 --> 01:05:41.375
[ Baby Cries ]
WHAT, WHAT ?

01:05:42.917 --> 01:05:46.083
HERE YOU GO.
COME ON.

01:05:46.083 --> 01:05:49.041
[ Cries Again ]
PLEASE ?

01:05:49.041 --> 01:05:51.667
[ Cries Louder ]

01:05:51.667 --> 01:05:54.625
YOU DON'T
WANT IT, HUH ?

01:05:54.625 --> 01:05:58.125
[ Continues Crying ]

01:05:58.125 --> 01:06:01.083
I JUST CHANGED
YOU.
HUH ?

01:06:01.083 --> 01:06:05.583
AND YOU'RE NOT HUNGRY.
WHAT ELSE IS THERE IN LIFE ?

01:06:08.583 --> 01:06:12.417
[ Rings ]

01:06:12.417 --> 01:06:15.375
I ALWAYS WANTED TO BE
A MUSICAL COMEDY STAR.

01:06:15.375 --> 01:06:17.125
- DID YOU EVER TRY ?
- NO.

01:06:20.000 --> 01:06:23.375
[ Loudspeaker ]
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

01:06:23.375 --> 01:06:26.125
ACT II WILL BEGIN
IN THREE MINUTES.

01:06:28.834 --> 01:06:31.625
MICHAEL, HAVE YOU
EVER DONE ANY ACTING ?

01:06:31.625 --> 01:06:35.291
NO, NO, I LEAVE THAT
TO JACK.
THE IDIOT.

01:06:35.291 --> 01:06:40.375
[ Rings ]

01:06:40.375 --> 01:06:42.458
â™ª I GOT SUNSHINE â™ª

01:06:42.458 --> 01:06:44.166
â™ª ON A CLOUDY DAY â™ª

01:06:44.166 --> 01:06:46.041
â™ª WHEN IT'S COLD OUTSIDE â™ª

01:06:46.041 --> 01:06:48.667
â™ª I GOT THE MONTH OF MAY â™ª

01:06:48.667 --> 01:06:52.458
â™ª I GUESS YOU SAY â™ª

01:06:52.458 --> 01:06:55.792
â™ª WHAT CAN MAKE ME
FEEL THIS WAY â™ª

01:06:55.792 --> 01:06:57.166
â™ª MY GIRL â™ª

01:06:57.166 --> 01:07:00.291
MAYBE HE FELL ASLEEP,
OR FELL AND HIT HIS HEAD.

01:07:00.291 --> 01:07:02.458
HE'S PROBABLY
UNCONSCIOUS.

01:07:02.458 --> 01:07:04.542
COME ON,
IT'S STARTED.

01:07:04.542 --> 01:07:06.208
- THERE'S AN EMERGENCY.
- IT'S TERRIBLE.

01:07:06.208 --> 01:07:07.792
- I HAD A GREAT TIME.
- SEE YOU AT P.J.'s.

01:07:07.792 --> 01:07:09.291
SING US A SONG
FROM THE 2nd ACT.

01:07:09.291 --> 01:07:12.792
ARE THEY ALWAYS
THIS STRANGE ?

01:07:12.792 --> 01:07:15.083
YES...

01:07:15.083 --> 01:07:18.542
SINCE THEY GOT INVOLVED
WITH ANOTHER WOMAN.

01:07:18.542 --> 01:07:21.250
WASN'T THAT FUN,
HUH ?
YES.

01:07:21.250 --> 01:07:22.583
OOH, COVER
THAT.

01:07:22.583 --> 01:07:24.959
JACK, WHERE
ARE YOU ?
JACK !

01:07:24.959 --> 01:07:27.583
I'M RIGHT HERE.
WHAT, WHAT ?

01:07:27.583 --> 01:07:29.166
WHAT ARE
YOU DOING ?

01:07:29.166 --> 01:07:32.125
WHAT'S IT LOOK LIKE
I'M DOING, PETER ?

01:07:32.125 --> 01:07:33.959
IS EVERYTHING
ALL RIGHT ?

01:07:33.959 --> 01:07:37.583
EVERYTHING'S FINE, YEAH.
WHY ARE YOU BACK SO SOON ?

01:07:37.583 --> 01:07:40.834
UH, WE THOUGHT THAT WE
MIGHT HAVE LEFT THE STOVE ON.

01:07:40.834 --> 01:07:42.959
NO, NO.
THE STOVE'S NOT ON.

01:07:42.959 --> 01:07:44.834
I THINK THAT UNCLES
PETER AND MICHAEL ...

01:07:44.834 --> 01:07:47.375
ARE HAVING A
NERVOUS BREAKDOWN.

01:07:47.375 --> 01:07:52.625
I CALLED, JACK.
I LET THE
PHONE RING FOR 5 MINUTES.

01:07:52.625 --> 01:07:54.166
WHY DIDN'T YOU
ANSWER THE PHONE ?

01:07:54.166 --> 01:07:56.875
WELL, BECAUSE MARY AND
I WERE TAKING A SHOWER,

01:07:56.875 --> 01:07:58.959
WEREN'T WE ?
WE
DIDN'T HEAR ANYTHING.

01:07:58.959 --> 01:08:01.500
ISN'T THAT THE
TRUTH, MADEMOISELLE ?

01:08:01.500 --> 01:08:05.166
[ Baby Gurgles ]

01:08:08.041 --> 01:08:10.041
OH, YOU ARE CUTE.

01:08:10.041 --> 01:08:13.208
I NEVER PUT A PHONE
IN A SHOWER BEFORE.

01:08:13.208 --> 01:08:15.709
DO YOU GET MANY
CALLS IN HERE ?

01:08:15.709 --> 01:08:18.375
A STEADY
STREAM.

01:08:32.542 --> 01:08:34.291
HERE.

01:08:38.082 --> 01:08:41.166
"COMMERCIAL DIRECTOR
HOSPITALIZED AFTER MUGGING."

01:08:41.166 --> 01:08:44.582
YEAH, TAKE A LOOK AT THIS.
IT'S YOUR FRIEND, PAUL MILNER.

01:08:44.582 --> 01:08:47.625
"DON'T LET THIS HAPPEN TO YOU.
BE AT THE PHONE BOOTH ...

01:08:47.625 --> 01:08:50.332
AT THE CORNER OF 81st AND
COLUMBUS AT 8 PM TONIGHT."

01:08:50.332 --> 01:08:54.582
THEY'RE TRYING TO
INTIMIDATE US.
I HATE THAT.

01:08:54.582 --> 01:08:56.457
I'VE HAD ENOUGH
OF THIS DOO-DOO !

01:08:56.457 --> 01:08:58.166
I WANT TO FINISH
THIS, OKAY ?

01:09:01.582 --> 01:09:04.166
WA-WA-WA-WA.

01:09:04.166 --> 01:09:07.082
[ Telephone Rings ]

01:09:10.542 --> 01:09:13.417
HELLO ?

01:09:13.417 --> 01:09:16.750
YEAH, WE GOT
YOUR MESSAGE.

01:09:16.750 --> 01:09:21.500
UH-UH.
NO GOOD.
WE DO IT OUR WAY.

01:09:21.500 --> 01:09:26.207
BECAUSE WE GOT THE STUFF, AND
IF YOU DON'T DO IT OUR WAY --

01:09:26.207 --> 01:09:29.959
COME ON !
SAY IT, SAY IT.

01:09:29.959 --> 01:09:33.166
WE FLUSH IT
DOWN THE TOILET !

01:09:33.166 --> 01:09:35.959
OKAY, NOW.
LISTEN,
AND LISTEN GOOD.

01:09:35.959 --> 01:09:39.625
THERE'S A
CONSTRUCTION SITE --

01:10:03.625 --> 01:10:06.625
[ Baby Gurgles ]

01:10:17.500 --> 01:10:19.667
[ Brakes Screech ]

01:10:24.208 --> 01:10:26.834
[ Car Accelerates,
Tires Screech ]

01:10:26.834 --> 01:10:30.208
CAR 20 FOLLOWING SUSPECTS,
SOUTH BOUND, CENTRAL PARK WEST.

01:10:41.834 --> 01:10:43.917
[ Brakes Squeal ]

01:10:45.166 --> 01:10:47.333
[ Brakes Squeal ]

01:10:47.333 --> 01:10:49.250
COME ON,
PETER !

01:10:51.542 --> 01:10:53.250
[ Car Honks ]

01:10:53.250 --> 01:10:55.667
[ Car Accelerates ]

01:10:55.667 --> 01:10:58.041
DAMN IT, JOE,
WE LOST THEM !

01:10:58.041 --> 01:11:00.125
I'VE GOT 3 BLOCKS
TO TURN AROUND !

01:11:00.125 --> 01:11:02.917
THAT WAS GREAT.
THAT WAS GREAT.

01:11:02.917 --> 01:11:05.542
EVERYBODY REMEMBER WHAT
THEY'RE SUPPOSED TO DO ?

01:11:05.542 --> 01:11:08.000
COME ON, PETER.
IT'S NOT
THAT COMPLICATED A PLAN.

01:11:08.000 --> 01:11:09.875
NEXT, HE'LL WANT US TO
SYNCHRONIZE OUR WATCHES.

01:11:09.875 --> 01:11:12.542
SHOULD WE
DO THAT ?

01:11:29.208 --> 01:11:32.375
YES, THANK YOU.
HELLO, SERGEANT MELKOWITZ.

01:11:32.375 --> 01:11:37.291
MY NAME IS JACK HOLDEN.
I THINK
YOU KNOW MY 2 ROOMMATES.

01:11:37.291 --> 01:11:39.792
I MUST HAVE BEEN CRAZY
TO AGREE WITH THAT GUY.

01:11:42.166 --> 01:11:44.959
"ORANGE ELEVATOR."
HERE IT IS.

01:11:56.125 --> 01:11:58.166
"CLOSE DOOR."

01:12:01.792 --> 01:12:04.208
OKAY.
15, PLEASE.

01:12:04.208 --> 01:12:06.083
15 ?

01:12:06.083 --> 01:12:08.417
I'M ALL
FILTHY.

01:12:14.041 --> 01:12:16.500
[ Baby Cries ]

01:12:18.458 --> 01:12:20.041
[ Baby Continues to Cry]

01:12:23.250 --> 01:12:25.291
[ Baby Still
Cries ]

01:12:25.291 --> 01:12:29.166
WHAT'S WRONG,
SWEETHEART ?

01:12:29.166 --> 01:12:32.375
COME HERE.
WHAT IS IT, HUH ?

01:12:35.834 --> 01:12:39.792
WELL, YOU SHOULD HAVE
TOLD ME BEFORE WE LEFT.

01:12:42.709 --> 01:12:46.083
OH, BOY.
THIS IS NOT A
GOOD TIME TO DO THIS.

01:12:46.083 --> 01:12:48.250
HOLD STILL.

01:12:48.250 --> 01:12:50.959
THERE YOU GO.

01:12:53.291 --> 01:12:54.834
MICHAEL !

01:12:54.834 --> 01:12:56.667
THEY'RE
HERE.

01:12:59.375 --> 01:13:01.208
YOU KNOW, THIS IS
REALLY AGGRAVATING.

01:13:01.208 --> 01:13:03.166
I'M HERE,
BY THE PIPES.

01:13:03.166 --> 01:13:04.583
I DON'T HAVE
A LOT OF TIME --

01:13:04.583 --> 01:13:07.417
HOLD IT,
JUST HOLD IT.

01:13:07.417 --> 01:13:10.625
LOOK, WHERE IS THE
STUFF ?
GIVE IT TO ME.

01:13:10.625 --> 01:13:12.667
IT'S IN THE
ELEVATOR.
OH, BULLSHIT !

01:13:12.667 --> 01:13:15.709
IT'S IN THE CONTROL PANEL.
CHECK FOR YOURSELF.

01:13:15.709 --> 01:13:18.959
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO,
BRING MY HANDY TOOL KIT HERE ?

01:13:18.959 --> 01:13:21.333
YOU REALIZE ...

01:13:21.333 --> 01:13:24.375
WE HAD ABSOLUTELY
NOTHING TO DO WITH THIS.

01:13:24.375 --> 01:13:28.208
WE HAD NO IDEA WHAT
WAS IN THE PACKAGE.

01:13:28.208 --> 01:13:30.500
I COULD'VE FIGURED
THAT OUT IN 4 SECONDS.

01:13:30.500 --> 01:13:34.041
I MEAN, YOU GUYS
DON'T BEHAVE LIKE PROS.

01:13:34.041 --> 01:13:37.041
RIGHT !
WE'RE NOT PROS.

01:13:37.041 --> 01:13:39.750
I JUST SAID THAT,
DIDN'T I ?

01:13:39.750 --> 01:13:41.792
WHY MAKE IT
SO COMPLICATED ?

01:13:41.792 --> 01:13:45.709
WE'VE NEVER
DONE THIS.

01:13:45.709 --> 01:13:48.166
I'VE
GOT IT !
GREAT.

01:13:48.166 --> 01:13:51.542
YOU'RE FORGIVEN,
THIS TIME.

01:13:51.542 --> 01:13:54.041
VERY WISE OF YOU
TO COOPERATE.

01:13:54.041 --> 01:13:55.542
GLAD
IT'S OVER.

01:13:55.542 --> 01:13:58.041
NO HAPPIER THAN
I AM, BELIEVE ME.

01:13:58.041 --> 01:14:01.041
DEALING WITH AMATEURS IS
A REAL PAIN IN THE ASS.

01:14:01.041 --> 01:14:03.875
SO IS DEALING
WITH PROFESSIONALS.

01:14:03.875 --> 01:14:04.834
NO DOUBT.

01:14:04.834 --> 01:14:06.208
[ Bang ]

01:14:08.291 --> 01:14:09.709
HEY, WHAT
IS THAT ?

01:14:09.709 --> 01:14:12.917
WHAT ARE YOU,
ABUSING MY TRUST HERE ?

01:14:12.917 --> 01:14:14.542
WHOA !
[ Crash ]

01:14:14.542 --> 01:14:16.959
THERE'S SOMEONE
IN THERE !
COME ON !

01:14:19.041 --> 01:14:21.625
[ Crash ]

01:14:21.625 --> 01:14:24.125
COME ON,
MICHAEL !

01:14:24.125 --> 01:14:26.417
OH, NO.
LOOK OUT !

01:14:31.750 --> 01:14:33.000
[ Slam ]

01:14:35.333 --> 01:14:37.667
I LOST MY
BALANCE.
YOU ALL
RIGHT ?

01:14:37.667 --> 01:14:39.667
DID YOU
GET IT ?
YEAH,
I GOT IT !

01:14:39.667 --> 01:14:40.667
[ Laughing ]

01:14:49.083 --> 01:14:50.750
[ Crash, Bang ]

01:14:50.750 --> 01:14:55.083
WHO'S DOING THIS ?
I WANT THAT CAMERA, PUNK !

01:14:58.000 --> 01:14:59.917
THERE'S
6 SWITCHES !

01:14:59.917 --> 01:15:02.959
AW, THESE GUYS
WRECKED MY DAY !

01:15:02.959 --> 01:15:04.000
[ Click ]

01:15:08.458 --> 01:15:11.583
JACK !
WHAT THE HELL
HAPPENED ?

01:15:11.583 --> 01:15:13.291
HE HIT THE
WRONG BUTTON.
HE WHAT ?

01:15:15.375 --> 01:15:17.750
- CAN IT GO ANY FASTER ?
- THIS IS IT !

01:15:17.750 --> 01:15:19.625
YOU PUNKS !

01:15:19.625 --> 01:15:22.959
JACK !

01:15:22.959 --> 01:15:24.500
JACK !

01:15:24.500 --> 01:15:26.792
NOWHERE TO RUN,
NOWHERE TO HIDE.

01:15:26.792 --> 01:15:30.792
I WANT THAT HOME MOVIE.
I'LL WAIT FOR YOU... I WANT IT !

01:15:30.792 --> 01:15:32.792
OH, NO.

01:15:32.792 --> 01:15:35.458
JACK !

01:15:35.458 --> 01:15:37.959
HIT THE BUTTON
ON THE LEFT !

01:15:37.959 --> 01:15:40.041
THE ONE ON THE
LEFT, JACK !

01:15:40.041 --> 01:15:41.291
WHAT, WHAT ?

01:15:41.291 --> 01:15:43.625
HIT THE BUTTON
ON THE LEFT  !

01:15:43.625 --> 01:15:45.792
THERE IS
NO LEFT.

01:15:48.000 --> 01:15:50.709
COME ON, GET
IT GOING FASTER !
I CAN'T !

01:15:50.709 --> 01:15:52.667
[ Click ]
PLEASE --

01:15:55.000 --> 01:15:58.959
WHAT'S THE MATTER ?
WHY IS THIS ELEVATOR STOPPED ?

01:15:58.959 --> 01:16:00.834
I GOT 'EM !

01:16:00.834 --> 01:16:03.375
- WHAT'S GOING ON ?
- IT JUST AIN'T RUNNIN'.

01:16:03.375 --> 01:16:05.917
- DID YOU HIT THE BUTTONS ?
- YEAH.
IT'S DEAD.

01:16:05.917 --> 01:16:11.000
UNCLES PETER AND MICHAEL WILL
BE PLENTY TICKED OFF WITH DADDY.

01:16:14.834 --> 01:16:19.333
AREN'T YOU GLAD
HE'S ON OUR SIDE ?

01:16:19.333 --> 01:16:21.542
YOU WAIT FOR ME !
I KNOW WHERE YOU LIVE !

01:16:23.458 --> 01:16:26.041
[ Police Sirens Below ]

01:16:26.041 --> 01:16:29.875
[ Police
Sirens ]

01:16:29.875 --> 01:16:32.875
[ Squealing Tires
and Brakes ]

01:16:32.875 --> 01:16:34.709
[ Sirens Continue ]

01:16:42.709 --> 01:16:44.542
OH, NO,
VINCE.

01:16:44.542 --> 01:16:48.667
WHY IS THIS HAPPENING ?
WHY IS THIS HAPPENING ?

01:16:48.667 --> 01:16:49.583
WHY ?

01:16:49.583 --> 01:16:51.625
IT'S OKAY, GUYS,
IT'S OKAY.

01:16:54.417 --> 01:16:58.000
HI.
ARE YOU
SERGEANT MELKOWITZ ?

01:16:58.000 --> 01:17:01.250
YEAH.
ARE YOU
THE FATHER ?

01:17:01.250 --> 01:17:03.500
YES, YES,
I AM.

01:17:03.500 --> 01:17:06.500
THANKS FOR
THE PHONE CALL.

01:17:06.500 --> 01:17:08.750
IT WAS
PETER'S IDEA.

